  "subject": "Fix plugin related issues",
  "commit_message": "Fix plugin related issues\n\n- fix issues that are showing up in the IDE problems tab:\n  - ignore extract-docker-file plugin executions that are executed\n    in eclipse-based IDE's (eclipse, vscode) because Dockerfile's\n    are only needed when building the docker images\n  - update groovy-maven-plugin (2.0 -> 2.1.1) to fix warning that\n    appears in Java 11+. In the future we should switch to the\n    gmavenplus plugin\n  - exclude csar files from being eligible for filtering by the\n    maven-resources-plugin in the asdc-controller module.\n    This fixes an IndexOutputBounds exception that otherwise occurs\n\nIssue-ID: SO-4201\nChange-Id: I8f6ff81f6850a0d56e5f1f2a71f35605c53ca5ec\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <Fiete.Ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
